  "title": "Application Nurse Specialist ( Ortho, OT Trained Nurse ) #HVN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Essential Duties and Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>·        Assists surgeons in performing surgical techniques in the field of sports medicine using Company’s instruments, implants and consumables</p><p>·        Guide surgeons in using new products and techniques</p><p>·        Ensures appropriate instruments and implants are at the hospital and complete before each use</p><p>·        Builds positive relationships with customers</p><p>·        Identifies customer needs and recommends appropriate products to address them</p><p>·        Maintains a thorough understanding of the product lines; updates, features, benefits, surgical techniques</p><p>·        Adheres to compliance policy and guidelines at all times</p><p><strong>Education and Experience:</strong></p><p>·        Degree in Nursing or medical qualification</p><p>·        3+ years related working experience</p><p>·        Registered nurse</p><p>·        Professional experience in the sports medicine field is advantageous</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
